  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You camouflage yourself near an amount of dirt, rock or stone that can cover your size, gaining a +10 bonus to Hide checks and becoming able to Hide while being observed for as long as you remain immobile. Creatures who can See (Through) Chakra gain a +5 bonus to Spot checks against you while you hide like this.<br><br>You can partially merge with any rock or stone formation that can physically contain your body to gain DR 5/-. You must maintain direct contact to the surface you use to hide in and/or merge with. If you lose direct contact, the technique ends.</p>\n\n\n\n",
